   "type": "text",
   "x": 40,
   "y": 404,
   "width": 1744.96,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "Nginx Proxy Manager terminates HTTPS and forwards to the dashboard and server containers, which stay on loopback. A peer joins the overlay, and the docker-network routing peer advertises the VLAN 85 subnet with masquerade so approved peers reach it through the tunnel.",
   "originalText": "Nginx Proxy Manager terminates HTTPS and forwards to the dashboard and server containers, which stay on loopback. A peer joins the overlay, and the docker-network routing peer advertises the VLAN 85 subnet with masquerade so approved peers reach it through the tunnel.",
